    <item>
      <title>How to make a cool presentation</title>
      <link>https://example.com/post/presentation/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Apr 2023 01:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://example.com/post/presentation/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Everyone wants to make cool presentations. How can we do that?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;details&gt;
  &lt;summary&gt;Content&lt;/summary&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creativity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Soft skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/details&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-creativiry&#34;&gt;1 Creativiry&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To make your presentation unique, you need to be talented.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What can you add:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Funny videos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Graphs and statistics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Memes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimalictic design.
















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;img1&#34; srcset=&#34;
